① Touch to wake up the door lock and make sure the keypad is lightening up; 
② Enter "*" twice; 
③ Enter the initial master PIN code "12345678" 
④ Press "#" to confirm; \ n⑤ Voice broadcast " entered the master mode, please modify the master PIN code"; 
⑥ Enter the new master PIN code and press "#" to confirm; 
⑦ Enter the new master PIN code again and press "#" to complete the modification.

① The door lock supports 2.4G Wi-Fi, and does not support 5G Wi-Fi; 
② If the router has both 2.4G and 5G Wi-Fi, please use different Wi-Fi names so as not to affect the door lock network connection and video intercom; 
③ The door lock does not support the same Wi-Fi name roaming public Wi-Fi environment, i.e. the Wi-Fi environment in many public places like companies, hotels, etc.; 
④ If the public Wi-Fi connection is the only choice, you can install a router with a separate Wi-Fi name, and connect the router to the public Wi-Fi network; 
⑤ If you use the connected self-own Wi-Fi without a password, network connection will not be allowed, please set a password and bind the door lock later
